d":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5176267fdd5e52528068abad9d9d383821949c04","tid":621701,"uid":37375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T17:39:32.000Z","msg":"比你係海外醫生黎到香港醫院都嚇撚死啦<br />\n病房長期爆上一百幾十%<br />\nA&amp;E以前有人沖入黎生仔<br />\n睇門診要跑數睇五分鐘就要趕人走<br />\n好 唔講做野啦<br />\n屌你咩一個劏房單位幾百萬？<br />\n邊個會留係哩個鬼城"},{"pid":"1957d08d01e0fd953debdce50640a5bfd8a376b5","tid":621701,"uid":6420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T17:42:07.000Z","msg":"增加海外醫生？<br />\n除左大陸之外仲會有咩醫生HA會請？<br />\n請個剩係講到英文既解決到HA唔夠醫生既問題咩<br />\n對政府黎講海外醫生=大陸醫生"},{"pid":"fe39bfd371918bc7b9febcb647309a4c33e2571d","tid":621701,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:21:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11771916d6020494742605c336d5173adcc6b46d","tid":621701,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:32:04.000Z","msg":"增加海外醫生即係增加支那醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n西方外國醫生駛唔駛離鄉別井去香港長做丫?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27cbc655a0ef73ddf92f82a3c0b72375553fbb64","tid":621701,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:38:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f2df9ed757a8b37ce1c670ac93b0a377b0d46ec","tid":621701,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}